      <title>塞内加尔总统巴西鲁·迪奥马耶·费耶宣誓就任新总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/senegal-s-bassirou-diomaye-faye-is-sworn-in-as-new-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[反对派领袖巴西鲁·迪奥马耶·法耶 (Bassirou Diomaye Faye) 出狱参加上个月的选举不到三周后，宣誓就任塞内加尔总统，成为非洲最年轻的民选领导人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/senegal-s-bassirou-diomaye-faye-is-sworn-in-as-new-president</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 11:45:34 GMT</pubDate>
